    "description": "Mu Shu, Moo Shu or Mu Xu, is a northern Chinese dish! Here we've enhanced the flavour with untraditional harissa paste, giving a spicy depth of flavour. Served in lettuce boats for the crunch factor. Under 600 calories.",
